Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:33.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:36.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:38.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with Trafalgar Law and \Nhave come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:42.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy entered a fighting competition \N- in which a winner will get the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:44.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Flare-Flare Fruit as the prize \N- and won the first round.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:47.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but now, he's heading for the palace\Nto take back Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:48.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who's been captured by Doflamingo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, underground Dressrosa,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:55.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp and the others started the \Noperation to take down Doflamingo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tail Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe we can pull it off\Nwithout me fighting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, guys!\NI, Usoland, am taking command now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our target is a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go frighten her out of her wits!\NFollow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lead the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get to the Executive Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze! I'm taking over this lift!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna learn to fight anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect me to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain and wind will rust my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you doing this?!\NYou're just a toy, what do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a peaceful country where...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my child can live happily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take Dressrosa back\Nfor the King Riku Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe this!\NEverybody's collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all happened in a blink of an eye,\Nin the Block D match!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody is about to stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The End of the Match?!\NA Surprising Result of Block D!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very bizarre ending for a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All 20-some surviving tough \Nfighters have suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,been knocked out for an unknown reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's never happened before\Nin the long history of the Corrida Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in the center of the ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can see the shadow of someone\Nwho is struggling to stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the winner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That person of the shadow has done all this?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:07:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rebecca who just stood to her feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The well-known warriors who we thought
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would dominate the Block D match,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're all still lying down on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Corrida Colosseum Battle Tournament -
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the last winner moving to the finals is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unbelievably, a convict gladiator \Nand a granddaughter of King Riku,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the blot in the history of Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Screw you!\N--I know she cheated!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of trick did you use, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check her body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cloud of dust enveloped the ring\Nall of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?!\NIn any event, Rebecca has won!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!\NWhat did she do to Cavendish-{\i1}sama{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral Orlumbus couldn't be \Nbeaten by such a little tramp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was The Slicing Winds of Rommel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slicing Winds?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NI bet you've never heard of it-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a mysterious incident\Nthat took place in the Rommel Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say winds that cut people \Nblew there every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:08:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWhat a bizarre story-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They dispatched the Navy soldiers right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the winds killed a lot of them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing they found \Nout at the end was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the wind was actually a man\Nwho called himself Hakuba-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is still at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after he left the Rommel Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuba kept terrorizing \Npeople in various towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wherever Hakuba appears,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this pirate is always there \Nat the same time-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from me!\NYou little bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's acting strange!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He fell asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's a sleepwalker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuba is, indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an alter-ego of Cavendish\Nthat awakens while he is sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Hakuba committed a crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NCavendish had no choice but set out to the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and became a pirate-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel sorry for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's enjoying the situation!\NHe'd take advantage of your sympathies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a great swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hakuba is far stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that, he falls asleep\Nwhen his alter-ego appears
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that nature wasn't suitable \Nfor a battle royal, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rebecca can't be a winner!\N--I'm sure she used a pistol or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check her out already and eliminate her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we inspect Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We always check her\Nmore strictly than the regulations demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her equipment is the poorest\Namong all the competitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Corrida Colosseum,\Nthe winner is the winner no matter who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our job to manipulate the facts\Nand spoil someone's victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won without landing a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one way to win a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, she wasn't just lucky -\Nshe was the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who fended off Hakuba's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't see anything!\NOnly you my great {\i1}senpai{\i0} could see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who it is, though,\NI can't let anybody have the Flare-Flare Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't wait any longer!\NI can finally fight now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the finals next!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cool! He's totally messing around with\Nthat mechanical guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Señor! Just kick that geek's ass already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You poor girls don't get \Nhow cool cyborgs are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look how pretty my mechanical body is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't get it at all!\NWhat's so cool about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Señor's look is\Nten-thousand times prettier than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of the way a man is,\Nyou immature flappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way a man is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This pacifier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this drool bib!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not wearing them to attract you tramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my style and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it represents the way I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we were wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of like the way you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am a man, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got to take you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:06.14,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,DRESSROSA ROYAL PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:09.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE SUIT CHAMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your granddaughter sure is lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to enter the competition\Nalong with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, King Riku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe a man who was once a king\Nfought for the Devil Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're quite desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rebecca!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the members of your family are\Ngoing too far today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was also Violet's betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NIt's too much to be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it some kind of anniversary?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're not aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what you did this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the report on Doflamingo's abdication
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the throne and the Seven Warlords \Nthat spread all over the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake. Just a false report.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I learned that the slight hope was\Njust a hoax,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it made me want to fight for everything\Nin this country again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That was why you made a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Viola was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, she is a calculating tramp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll never act purely on her emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's weighing her options.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is this top rookie\Nwho came to challenge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Warlord,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, there is someone who has \Ndemonic blood in his veins
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and grabbed all the limelight two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bitch is wishing those two \Nallied pirates will defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Law is barely alive now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Straw Hat Luffy will never come \Nout of the Colosseum as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And right now, as for the other \Nmembers of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyborg Franky is attacking the Toy House\Non his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think he can beat\Nthe executives of my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest - Pirate Hunter Zoro,\NFoxfire Kin'emon, Nico Robin,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Sniperking are still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think they can even reach\Nthe underground level.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hello, sir!\N--Oh! New recruits?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you! The job here is easy -\Nyou just push around the toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? That's good to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about this place\Nso can you teach me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:41.65,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,AT THE FOOT OF THE "KING'S PLATEAU"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a lift up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:50.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,LUFFY IN A CARP SUIT
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:53.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ZORO IN A CAT SUIT
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KIN'EMON IN A FROG SUIT
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.99,sign1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The palace where Doflamingo \Nis and the Toy House
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.99,sign1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Palace\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NThe Toy House
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the trade port where the \NSMILE factory are located -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:08.73,sign1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Palace\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NThe Toy House\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NThe Trade Port
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthey are all connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, if we can get into the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwe can go to the Toy House and the factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To go to the factory, \Nyou have to pass through
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Neither the palace or the Toy House.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my colleagues must've \Nsnuck into the trade port
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthrough the secret passage that we dug.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta go to the palace first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still can't get over how
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are such small people\Neven though I see one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she looks like a toy!\NHow interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were tons of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Let me meet them later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't do this often!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only show ourselves\Nto the Big Humans of the royal family
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you Usolanders, aka the Straw Hats,\Nare the exception!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:21:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usolanders?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain everything later!\NOperation SOP is already underway!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the lift to the \Nentrance of the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go that high with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To enter the lift, we have to show a pass\Nto a security guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just kick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do such a thing, it's gonna be messy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand we'll have to face more enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.21,0:22:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so bad about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bubblehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure about these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to the blockhead who gets lost easily,\NI'm with a witless bubblehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you call a blockhead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is somebody there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.90,0:22:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They already know that we're here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.24,0:22:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.67,0:22:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Straw Hat Luffy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:22:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI'll help you enter to the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
